<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.5">
<l>vaṇkai yāṉavu ṇarkku nāyakaṉ vēḷvi</l>
<l>yilceṉṟu māṇiyāy</l>
<l>maṇkai yāliran tāṉma rāmara mēḻu</l>
<l>meytava lattiṉāṉ</l>
<l>eṇkai yāṉima yattuḷ ḷāṉiruñ cōlai</l>
<l>mēviya vempirāṉ</l>
<l>tiṇkaim mātuyar tīrtta vaṉtiru vēṅka</l>
<l>ṭamaṭai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, take refuge at Tiruvēṅkaṭam of him who ended the sorrow</l>
<l rend="indent">of the beast with a powerful hand[-like trunk],</l>
<l>Our lord who dwells in Iruñcōlai, he who is in the Himalayas,</l>
<l rend="indent">he with eight hands,</l>
<l>The strong one who shot seven fig trees, the one who begged</l>
<l rend="indent">with [his] hands for land</l>
<l>As a dwarf appearing at the sacrifice of him of liberal hands,</l>
<l rend="indent">the leader of demons.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
